Nollywood actor, Blossom Chukwujekwu, on Friday announced his marriage to Ehinome Akhuemokhan. The actor disclosed this on Friday via his Instagram page, with pictures of his traditional wedding. Recall that this is Chukwujekwu’s second marriage, as he was once married to media personality and fashion designer, Maureen Esisi for four years before their divorce in 2020. -Advertisement- Celebrities took to his Instagram page to congratulate the couple. @Kehindebankole wrote, “Congratulations to a perfect gentleman I know.” @omonioboli wrote, “Congratulations Blossom.” @ Chief_femibranch wrote, “Congrats bro of mine.” @gideonokeke.ng wrote. “Bro…just BLOSSOM!” POLL